Name: [Costume] Sculptor - Checkmate
Skins.Des: Will castling be the winning move?

Name: [Costume] Enchantress - Maroon Crystal
Skins.Des: By the time the Lost Girl had seen through the lies and betrayal, the land of Oz had long been decayed. Unwilling to give in, she will step into the maroon crystal shoes and return to this strange path.

Name: [Costume] Geisha - Lady Thirteen
Skins.Des: For a beautiful woman who lived in a foreign country, perhaps the only way for her to keep herself safe... is to obtain sufficient leverage on people. Lady Thirteen always said, “Kindness alone withers the roses. Only the valuable nutrients will keep roses alive.“

Name: [Costume] Violinist - Inferno Sonata
Skins.Des: No one can resist the willpower embedded by the visitor from hell in the music piece. Yet the musician only cares about the elegant purity and isn't flattered by the boisterous sound. It's only when he finds out that a misfit has fled to the world of the living in pursuit of his music that he's finally motivated to play his heart out.

Name: [Costume] Batter - Lava Cake
Skins.Des: A fighter who won't succumb to desire and pleasure. Instead of wallowing in the illusion of contentment, he chooses to break out of the sweet confinement of joy and search for an unconfined world.

Name: [Costume] Smiley Face - Netherwalker
Skins.Des: Pickman only took what he saw in the Nether as inspiration, and somehow those fools couldn't get enough of his work. When he discovered that the Vile Blossom's deteriorating erosion can only be transferred and can't be eliminated, he chose to be the container himself. But who can ever replace her as Pickman's model?

Name: [Costume] Gamekeeper - Molten Hound
Skins.Des: It should have been the best vessel, yet it devoured the 'prize' from its first victory. Driven by instinct, it swept away the racers who were fighting for themselves on each racecourse.

Name: [Costume] Bloody Queen - Isabella
Skins.Des: Isabella's Costume

Skins.Des: Indulging in the marvels of engineering and feeding his insatiable desire for cybernetic enhancements, he relishes between the pain and pleasure brought by body aumentation.

Name: [Costume] Ripper - Count's Banquet
Skins.Des: The Count lived in seclusion in the old castle, and his bloodthirsty instincts have long been drowned by emptiness and loneliness. Eventually, when everyone forgot the Bloodline Count's name, the banquet invitation from the castle set off a new shockwave.

Name: [Costume] Acrobat - ACE
Skins.Des: Tie-breaker. Are you going to win this round?

Name: [Costume] Doctor - Mikan Tsumiki
Skins.Des: An introverted Hope's Peak student from the class of 77, also known as the “Ultimate Nurse”

Name: [Costume] Mechanic - Chiaki Nanami
Skins.Des: A Hope's Peak student in the class of 77, also known as the “Ultimate Gamer”. She's the kind of student who is exceptionally focused when playing games but a sleepy head when not

Name: [Costume] Mercenary - Nagito Komaeda
Skins.Des: A Hope's Peak student in the class of 77, also known as the “Ultimate Lucky Student”. Even in hopeless situations, his faith in his companions never flaters.

Name: [Costume] Smiley Face - Oven
Skins.Des: There's no absolute truth, just as there's no pure deception. Only those who allow their soul to indulge will acquire lasting fulfillment.

Name: [Costume] Gravekeeper - Cheese
Skins.Des: A piece of soft and peculiar cheese, nothing more. Despite it being the first dish coming out of the oven, its sense of inferiority diminishes its courage to escape from utopia.

Name: [Costume] Mechanic - Puppeteer
Skins.Des: She never figured out why the Investigation Bureau sealed off the Secrets of the Abyss, until the Netherwalker's existence made her realise the catastrophe if it is ever revealed. But the Abyss will no doubt find a way to show itself, and just when she's willing to step up...

Name: [Costume] Cowboy - Whiplash
Skins.Des: At the exit on the other side, the veteran's last lesson for the newcomer is about choice: take on everything alone and stay behind, or accept the horrible price and leave. No matter which choice is made, it will only bring him closer to the Netherwalker.

Name: [Costume] Embalmer - Trickster
Skins.Des: The Trickster tried his best to protect the Surveyors mind from being eroded, just so they could continue with their journey on the road of darkness with the Abyss' creation in their hands. Yet, his playful miscommunication finally took its toll on the Puppeteer.

Name: [Costume] Seer - Surveyor
Skins.Des: The admirers call it the Nether, while the opponents call it the Abyss. To the Surveyor, this is how the indiscernible manipulate people's mind, so that the admirers become strong and the opponents shrink in fear. The erosion of mind and engraving of flesh through art is nothing but another of their hobbies.

Name: [Costume] Barmaid - Fueling Agent
Skins.Des: An agent of the Energy Corporation. She secretly works as an experimenter for the Pharmaceutical Corporation. She understands that just like fueling agents can be applied to engines, enhancers can be used on racers, but the kind of spirit they're looking for can only be identified through tragic and fierce competitions.

Name: [Costume] Priestess - Reflective Mirror
Skins.Des: An agent of the Pharmaceutical Corporation. She uses the reflection in her mirror to find hidden shortcuts in the Garden Corridor. She realized long ago that she is merely a stepping stone for the company to investigate the disobedient monsters.

Name: [Costume] Acrobat - Pumping Tires
Skins.Des: An agent of the Transportation Corporation. He is well-prepared for the Wintry Harbor race track: No matter the cost, he is adamant in uncovering the secrets hidden behind this racetrack in order to put an end to this testing ground for conspiracies.

Name: [Costume] Prospector - Highway Cavalier
Skins.Des: Having once worked for the transportation corporation, he is adamant that he is the last true racer of his time who wishes to complete each race with the simplest sportsmanship - despite the significant pain and failure he has suffered.

Name: Wu Chang - Frost
Skins.Des: Passion only brings a full head of steam that destroys one's process of thinking. A rational thinker must stay cool and calm at all times.

Name: Forward - Locomotive
Skins.Des: The train he vowed to protect never reached the station. When the world is frozen still, the interminable engine he carries shall power the last train that has no terminus.

Name: Smiley Face - Scarecrow
Skins.Des: It's a scarecrow outfit found near the exit gate. Although it was on fire, I thought it could be salvaged.

Name: [Costume] Prisoner - Electrolysis
Skins.Des: He made use of the delicate relationship between science and alchemy to complete the performance of turning stone into gold, yet he has no idea that the real Philosopher's Stone is nothing but a glorified lie.

Name: [Costume] Thief - Deputy
Skins.Des: The tears of innocence and the feathers of lust - I hope you measure their weights before the judgment day comes.

Name: [Costume] Mind's Eye - Clerk
Skins.Des: Wisdom is the source of all conflicts, and ignorance is the annotation of all sins.

Name: [Costume] Seer - Final Honor
Skins.Des: After a horrible riot, the region he guarded was in decline. Yet despite the notoriety, he insisted on sending out this secret letter.

Name: [Costume] Feaster - Exoplanet
Skins.Des: Knowledge changes one's fate is an inescapable truth. Are you willing to exchange your soul for a little taboo that can stir up a storm?

Name: [Costume] Guard 26 - Mr. Eggshell
Skins.Des: He wanted to stay in the peaceful dream forever, yet when he was forced to wake up from his dream abruptly, he realized he wanted to protect was ruined.

Name: [Costume] Violinist - Ouroboros
Skins.Des: In order to harvest the essence generated from the displacement of body and soul, the Ouroboros is cursed with the fate of devouring itself.

Name: [Costume] Prospector - Ronald Of Ness
Skins.Des: It's you, the strings that weave our destiny - let it become the web that entangles us all.

Name: [Costume] Herald - Princess Ozma
Skins.Des: Those in true power fabricate one elaborate lie after another to absorb their prey's life essence when they are most vulnerable.

Name: [Costume] Entomologist - The Wicked Witch
Skins.Des: Despite being deceived, framed, and imprisoned in a lonely tower, she still hasn't given up the name she once had, and the person she once was.

Name: [Costume] Mad Eyes - Scrooge
Skins.Des: When the ropes of destiny intertwine, who would become our Atropos?

Name: [Costume] Mechanic - Re-Swim
Skins.Des: Do you prefer the cheer at the end of the lane or the silence beneath the waves

Name: [Costume] Photographer - En Ligne
Skins.Des: Are you ready to pierce the illusion?

Name: [Costume] Postman - Keyboard
Skins.Des: A misfit who's crazy about music, he can't stand the harsh rules and inequality of the sound of hell any longer, so he banished himself to the world of the living. He comes across a quirky bar on the way and is attracted by music that reminded him of home. Yet he never thought he's about stepping into a trap that may cost him his faith

Name: [Costume] Evil Reptilian - Bone Flute
Skins.Des: When he's hunting down the fleeing demons, the flute embedded in his body will begin emitting steam, sounding off terrifying piping noises. The noises symbolize the wailing left behind by the hunted. For his next target, he hunts the ones who have given up morality.

Name: [Costume] Wu Chang - Flying Guillotine
Skins.Des: As destiny pushes him off a cliff, the cries of the gentle, even at the top of their lungs, won't turn back time. As the dust settled... perhaps... remaining calm is the ultimate answer.

Name: [Costume] Prospector - Sparrow
Skins.Des: It's only natural that a child who has never seen kindness will treasure his hard-earned candy. Trying to blend into adults' world, learning to disguise, but perhaps...she's still the one who understands his value and dreams.

Name: [Costume] Barmaid - Enoshima Junko
Skins.Des: A student in Hope's Peak Academy's Class 78th, the “Ultimate Fashionista“. Her true identity is actually...

Name: [Costume] Lucky Guy - Makoto Naegi

Name: Pass Card
pass
passcard
skip
passquestion
skipquestion
PowerUps.Usage: This item is useable in the commands `$prefixquick` and `$prefixhunt`... Once you run one of those commands and feel like not being able to answer the question given, use your Pass Card by typing 'Pass' in the chat

Name: Reveal Card
reveal
revealcard
reveal-card
revealanswer
PowerUps.Usage: Reveal Cards are useable in `$prefixquick` and `$prefixhunt` commands and it gives you the ability to reveal the answer of the question you're stuck in... The answer is revealed at the end of the embed's description, powerups can't be used twice on one question!

Name: Switch Card
switchcard
switch
switchquestion
PowerUps.Usage: Use this powerup when you encounter a hard question you can't answer in the `$prefixhunt` or `$prefixquick` commands to make the bot switch to another question... Powerups can only be used once per question

Name: Black Mud
blackmud
mud
mudbomb
PowerUps.Usage:
This powerup is useable via the command `$prefixuse` and it allows you to throw a mud-ball at your friend's `logicpath` profile
The effect lasts for **24 hours** but can be removed by using the **Excitement-Powerup**

**Usage:** `$prefixuse mud <user>`

Name: Cooldown Minimizer
cooldownminimizer
speed
speedpill
speedpotion
cooldown
PowerUps.Usage:
This powerup minimizes the cooldowns for all commands... The percentage of the cooldowns' reducement is randomized, it can be either **10%**, **30%** or **50%**...
To use this powerup, do `$prefixuse cooldownMinimizer`... The effect lasts for **1 hour** and Can't be stacked.

Name: Excitement
excitement
exc
exitment
PowerUps.Usage:
Use this powerup to remove negative effects/powerups put on you by other users...
This powerup removes the effect of Black Mud...
Do `$prefixuse excitement` to remove the effect
